	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName> <date>15<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Augt.&#47;59</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Pha</p>
				<p>Rev. DrSir&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Your esteemed Letter<lb/> I duly received and communicated<lb/> its contents&#8212;in as far as they<lb/> concern him&#8212;to <persName>Mr Benjamin</persName><lb/> who intends to write to you<lb/> direct.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">In consequence of your<lb/> remarks&#44; I got the Israelite<lb/> and read the article in<lb/> question.  It is&#44; as usual a<lb/> gross fraud&#44; &#38; an impudent<lb/> speculation on the ignorance<lb/> of the public.  I hold the<lb/> man &#38; his paper in too<lb/> great contempt to be<lb/> moved by any thing he</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>writes.  Still we have a<lb/> public duty to perform to the<lb/> illustrious dead&#44; and must<lb/> not permit the Israelite to<lb/> claim fellowship with Rambam<add>&#63;</add>.<lb/>  I will therefore send you<lb/> in the course of this week&#8212;say<lb/> on <date>Wednesday</date> or <date>Thursday</date>&#8212;a<lb/> paper on &#8220;Jewish doctrine&#8221;<lb/> &#8220;<persName>Maimonides</persName> on a future<lb/> state&#44; Repentance&#44; and the<lb/> resurrection of the dead&#8221;<lb/>  which I trust&#44; in addition<lb/> to disposing of the &#8220;Israelite&#8221; will<lb/> have the merit of a word in<lb/> season for the <add>Hebrew</add></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I shall want a Bible<lb/> to give away.  What is the<lb/> very lowest price for a copy<lb/> plainly bound.&#63;[sic]</p>
			<pb n="3"/>
			<p rend="indent(1)">If you think well of the<lb/> paper I am about to send<lb/> you try to get it inserted<lb/> into some <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName> paper<lb/> I myself will take charge of<lb/> <placeName>St Louis</placeName>&#8212;formerly one of the<lb/> &#8220;Israelites&#8221; strongholds&#44; but<lb/> where now thank God his<lb/> <hi rend="underline">prestige</hi> is gone</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">Yours very respfy</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)"><persName role="author">M J Raphall</persName></p>
			<pb n="4"/>
				<p><add>&#63;</add></p>
